headline: Q3 Earnings Highlights: Autodesk (NASDAQ:ADSK) Vs The Rest Of The Design Software Stocks
summary: As the Q3 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the design software industry, including Autodesk (NASDAQ:ADSK) and its peers.
